The Nightars (Revived) Mod

Author: Seth Boyce (AbsoluteXero/AbsoluteXeroEX)

The content presented herein was originally created by Starbound Community user, iMisterX. This mod is now being continued by the author listed above. Any assets present may be used with or without permission; although no notice of derivative use is required, please ensure that any similar item names (JSON: "itemName") are changed so as not to conflict with these assets. This mod may include assets that may not work without the support of other mods (i.e., Frackin' Universe, Ztarbound, etc.), but they should not cause any issues with vanilla-based gameplay.

Any updates to the mod will be made publicly available with detail as they are pushed. Any issues should be brought to AbsoluteXero (GitHub: AbsoluteXeroEX).
